Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.42,0:00:09.38,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Stala sa tu vražda...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.11,0:00:30.32,Rena,,0,0,0,,Stalo sa ti niečo? Stalo?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.64,0:00:33.80,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Vystrašila si ma.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.80,0:00:37.24,Rena,,0,0,0,,Povedal si mi že potrebujeme sekeru alebo niečo také...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.24,0:00:38.18,Rena,,0,0,0,,Preto som...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.40,0:00:41.11,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Preto si doniesla jednu veľkú.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.11,0:00:44.00,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Ale už sa stmieva. Nechajme to na zajtra.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.34,0:00:49.50,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,No tak...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.50,0:00:52.21,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Plukovník nás tu počká.
