Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.16,0:09:11.41,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Vrahyňou je Rika!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.24,0:09:13.70,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Použila jed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:16.50,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,A vraždila v ordinácii!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.25,0:09:18.33,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Do peklááá!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.33,0:09:20.04,Satoko,,0,0,0,,Ja to nechápem!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:23.50,Rika,,0,0,0,,Mám rada pomalú smrť jedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.67,0:09:26.01,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Bolo to ľahké.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.92,0:09:29.97,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Žiadam odvetu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.68,0:09:32.97,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Ale najprv musím ísť na záchod.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.97,0:09:35.39,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Môžeš sa tam ľutovať koľko chceš.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.14,0:09:38.44,Mion_Shion,,0,0,0,,Mii-chan, to bolo hrubé!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.44,0:09:42.10,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Nie. Tentoraz si idem premyslieť svoju stratégiu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.11,0:09:43.40,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Maebara-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.70,0:09:47.82,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Máš návštevu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.82,0:09:49.82,Anyone,,0,0,0,,Čaká ťa pri vchode.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.37,0:09:51.70,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Návštevu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.29,0:09:59.75,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,Ty si Maebara? Keiichi Maebara?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.75,0:10:02.83,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,To som ja. A vy ste?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:08.34,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,V aute som zapol klimatizáciu. Čo keby sme sa porozprávali tam?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.38,0:10:13.72,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Takže, čo odo mňa chcete?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.18,0:10:18.73,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,Povedz mi čo vieš o tomto mužovi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.77,0:10:23.10,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,To je... pán Tomitake?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.10,0:10:26.07,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,Dobre. A vieš aj kto je táto žena?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.03,0:10:33.07,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Totiž... Neviem ako sa volá, ale minulú noc som ju videl s Tomitakeom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.45,0:10:36.58,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,Kedy si ich videl naposledy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.20,0:10:41.46,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Videl som ich minulú noc, po Oslave Sviatku Česania Vlny.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.54,0:10:45.58,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,Všimol si si niečo zvláštne?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.88,0:10:49.42,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,Povedz mi, prosím, všetko čo vieš.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.42,0:10:51.59,Keiichi,,0,0,0,,Stalo sa im niečo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.59,0:10:54.45,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,Muž na obrázku počas tejto noci
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.45,0:10:56.10,Oishi Kuraudo,,0,0,0,,zomrel.
